==Description==
'''Leopold''' is a camel living on [[Desert Island]]. He is often seen near the [[Hacienda]] with his owner, a [[grobo]]. He loves sand roses he gets from his owner.

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==
Leopold didn't play any role in [[Twinsen]]'s adventure, apart form giving him hints.

==Trivia==
Leopold was imported to the [[Island of the White Leaf Desert]]. It is unknown where he came from, as there is no other island on [[Twinsun]] where there are camels.

